reviewText: Some of Drew Barrymore's cutest films, bargain price for 4 movies too! Bought it for Music and Lyrics which is hard to find,rest are a bonus!
Received one DVD. with only one of the eight movies advertised on the DVD.
We bought this primarily for the movie The Wedding Singer which is a great movie!  Getting 3 others that we hadn't seen in many other years was just a bonus.  Each movie is on its own separate disc.
These are some of Drew's weaker performances, but a must for the Drew Barrymore fan.
I love this set of movies!
